{"id": "1525368699010158673", "channel_id": "1350058928020656178", "author_id": "642780768577519616", "author_name": "entipathas", "content": "In 6-11, for the cats event, the \"Follow them\" choice should be capitalized as \"Follow Them\" to be consistent.\nIn the text after choosing the \"Follow them\" choice, a period is missing after \"even if the dark traps lie ahead\"\nAlso, I think \"the\" in \"even if the dark traps lie ahead\" should be removed, since \"the\" implies specific traps that are known of (and there don't seem to be any in this case).\n\"even if the dark traps lie ahead\" -> \"even if dark traps lie ahead.\"", "timestamp": "2026-07-11T05:10:37.824000+00:00", "thread_id": "1350058928020656178", "attachments": [{"id": "1525368698276151437", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1482271, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350058928020656178/1525368698276151437/image.png?ex=6a54734d&is=6a5321cd&hm=02f664ea2bdfccb0c4d8e5a455412fc240a2fa90563fa1f88ac4b0f10b881122&"}, {"id": "1525368698691649547", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 784747, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1350058928020656178/1525368698691649547/image.png?ex=6a54734d&is=6a5321cd&hm=e982969cb7e4e7df2c245d723a7735ff836e64e7c535358fcb700ede9f81c9ff&"}]}
